Listerine Advanced White voting is closed|http://www.glamour.co.za|https://www.glamour.co.za/2018/09/voting-closed-listerine-advanced-white/|listerine advanced white|2018-09-11|September||We loved watching the videos of the top 10 entrants in our Style Your Smile competition, with Listerine Advanced White. Their stories were inspiring and it’s so fabulous to see that their smiles give them confidence.

After keeping an eye on the tons of votes that we’ve received, it’s quite clear that you GLAMOUR girls enjoyed the videos too. However, bear in mind that voting is now closed.

One lucky voter will walk away with a prize worth R5 000, which includes a mall voucher and handy Listerine Advanced White goodies. Will it be you?

Stay tuned to our social media channels to find out because we’ll unveil the winner today, 11 September!
